<style>
  .article_column-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 320px;
    border-radius: 11px;
  }
  img.article_column-image {
    overflow: hidden;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: 50% 50%;
  }
  .article_column-image-border {
    border: 1px solid rgba(60, 31, 27, 0.30);
  }
  .article_column {
      height: max-content;
  }
  .article_column-third {
    width: calc(33.3333334% - 33.3333334px);
  }
  .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 25px);
  }
  .article_column-text-third-top {
    padding-top: 81px;
  }
  @media(max-width: 1450px) {
    .article_column-half {
    width: calc(50% - 15px);
  }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
      gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 1250px) {
    .article_column-third {
        width: calc(50% - 15px);
    }
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 81px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 950px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 114px;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 750px) {
    .article_column-text-third-top {
      padding-top: 0;
    }
    .article_column-half {
      width: 100%
    }
    .article_column-third {
        width: 100%;
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .article_columns-wrapp {
        gap: 30px;
    }
    .rebranding_container {
        gap: 40px;
    }
    .article_column-text .h3-heading-pp, .article_column-text .h3-heading-ss {
        text-align: center;
    }
  }
  @media(max-width: 450px) {
    .article_column-image {
      height: 250px;
    }
  }
</style>
<div class="rebranding_container block-flex-wrap block-gap-50">
  <div class="rebranding-section-title block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
    <h2 class="h2-heading-ss">
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
       World's best 
      </span>
      Louis Vuitton handbags 
      <span class="h2-heading-pp">
       authenticators at your hands
      </span>
    </h2>
  </div>
  <div class="article_columns-wrapp block-flex-wrap block-gap-50 block-flex-start-start">
    <div class="article_column article_column-half article_column-text-half block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Authentic Louis Vuitton handbags often feature date codes, which can be difficult to read or even missing in older handbags. Understanding these codes is essential for verifying the authenticity and history of Louis Vuitton products.
          <br><br>
          Authenticate your branded items with Experts & AI. For potential buyers, understanding the details of a Louis Vuitton handbag, such as date codes, is crucial.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="article_column article_column-half article_column-text-half block-flex-wrap block-gap-30">
      <div class="article_column-text block-flex-wrap block-gap-15 block-flex-center-center">
        <p class="article_column-desc body-text taj w-100">
          Additionally, understanding the details of Louis Vuitton products, including accessories and clothing, is crucial for authentication. Authenticating Louis Vuitton handbags involves discussing essential details and expert tips to ensure legitimacy. 
          <br><br>
          The desirability and high demand for Louis Vuitton products highlight their exceptional quality, timeless design, and status as luxury items.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
  {
    "name": "Three text columns",
    "class": "article_columns article_three-columns article_three-text-columns rebranding-wider-section",
    "settings": []
  }
{% endschema %}